Meet Ecosphere.
Ecosphere Technologies, Inc. (OTCBB:ESPH) is an innovative U.S. technology licensing and manufacturing company that develops environmental solutions for global markets. We help industry increase production, reduce costs, and protect the environment through a portfolio of more than 35 powerful, patented and patent pending, technologies: Technologies like Ozonix® and our Ecos PowerCube®, which are being licensed across a diverse range of industries and applications throughout the world.
Read More









Water Processed
Every day, businesses around the globe rely on Ecosphere Technologies’ advanced water recycling technologies and expertise to help them reclaim and reuse water, ensuring that they are meeting both their financial and environmental obligations.
Contact us


Recycled Water

Eliminated Chemical Biocide










Ozonix
Chemical-Free Water Recycling
Many water recycling processes rely on chemicals – chemicals that
            are both costly and harmful to the environment. Ecosphere’s Ozonix®
            Technology offers customers and partners a chemical-free alternative
            to high-volume water recycling for a diverse range of applications
            ranging from the oil & natural gas industry and mining, to 
            agriculture, municipal, and industrial wastewater treatment.
Learn more about how Ozonix® can help your business solve its 
            most pressing water management challenges through environmentally 
            responsible water and wastewater treatment, water recycling, and 
            water reuse.
