We Help Mining Operations:

Recycle, reuse and conserve water resources
Increase mining and mineral resource recovery rates 
Develop new unproven energy and mining reserves as well as increase productivity and recovery in existing energy and hard mineral operations
Eliminate the use of toxic chemical biocides and cyanides, further eliminating health, safety and environmental (HSE) issues associated with chemical consumption, transportation and handling
Promote water conservation and the protection of surrounding water resources and heritage lands
Comply with increasingly stringent regulations

 

 




