Companies
Ecosphere Technologies, Inc.
 






Ecosphere Technologies, Inc. (OTCBB:ESPH) is an innovative U.S. technology licensing and manufacturing company that develops environmental solutions for global markets. We help industry increase production, reduce costs, and protect the environment through a portfolio of more than 35 powerful, patented and patent pending, technologies: Technologies like Ozonix and our Ecos PowerCube, which are being licensed across a diverse range of industries and applications throughout the world.

