			Company Description 


			Ecosphere Technologies, Inc. engages in the development of patented solutions for the global water, agriculture, energy and industrial markets. Its portfolio includes  Ozonix, the Ecos PowerCube, and the Ecos GrowCube. The company was founded by Dennis E. McGuire and Jacqueline K. McGuire in April 1...
		


                Ecosphere Technologies, Inc. engages in the development of patented solutions for the global water, agriculture, energy and industrial markets. Its portfolio includes  Ozonix, the Ecos PowerCube, and the Ecos GrowCube. The company was founded by Dennis E. McGuire and Jacqueline K. McGuire in April 1998 and is headquartered in Stuart, FL.
            




