Ecos GrowCube - Fully-Automated Hydroponic Greenhouse






 
In its simplest form, the Ecos GrowCube is a turn-key, fully-automated hydroponic greenhouse that is Made in the USA and fabricated out of aircraft-grade aluminum. An Ecos GrowCube utilizes hydroponic growing techniques in order to maximize the amount of crop production possible in a given footprint and eliminates the need for soil, fossil fuels, pesticides and toxic chemicals. Ecosphere’s patented OZONIX INSIDE technology is also utilized to...
 
 
 
 




